  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434880/extras/62a625f8de9a184b79f4fa80356f34d4.avif?t=1753023152\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>⌁ Incoming transmission to Earth! ⌁</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm MAXCYBER. ROBO OH is an FC-style robots fighting game. Play as more than 12 great robots in a grand tournament to declare the king. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A modernized fighting system is combined with a retro control scheme. Perform simple or advanced combos to uncover each robot's full potential. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm waiting for your fight! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434880/extras/a2d79b6f5c05a49387f0ce1edf40ca0b.avif?t=1753023152\" width=600 height=296 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More Than 12 Playable Robots</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VS, Arcade, Endless, Training modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All-Original Graphics And Sound</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden Characters And Special Boss Events</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434880/extras/890b3e198544d6a66c3d2214957392b6.avif?t=1753023152\" width=600 height=260 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434880/extras/62a625f8de9a184b79f4fa80356f34d4.avif?t=1753023152\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>⌁ Incoming transmission to Earth! ⌁</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm MAXCYBER. ROBO OH is an FC-style robots fighting game. Play as more than 12 great robots in a grand tournament to declare the king. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A modernized fighting system is combined with a retro control scheme. Perform simple or advanced combos to uncover each robot's full potential. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm waiting for your fight! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434880/extras/a2d79b6f5c05a49387f0ce1edf40ca0b.avif?t=1753023152\" width=600 height=296 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More Than 12 Playable Robots</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VS, Arcade, Endless, Training modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All-Original Graphics And Sound</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden Characters And Special Boss Events</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1434880/extras/890b3e198544d6a66c3d2214957392b6.avif?t=1753023152\" width=600 height=260 /></span></p>",
